JUST ANNOUNCED!
Comedian Rene Vaca w/ Special Guest - Sunday 9/10 @ The Well Comedy Club

Rene Vaca is back by popular demand! You e seen Rene exploding on TikTok and Instagram, now come see him LIVE! Standup NBC winner Rene Vaca was born and raised in the San Fernando Valley in southern California. After his father was incarcerated, he started his own landscaping business at the age of 15. That came to an end when he was accepted to the University of California, Merced. Vaca has since been pursuing his dream in stand-up comedy and recently just won the 16th annual StandUp NBC competition! He has shared the stage with revered industry comedians such as Bill Burr, Ken Jeong, Amir K., Jamie Kennedy more.
